## Ultimate DuinoBits Starter Kit

SKU: STARTER

0 Reviews
[Add Review](http://duinobits.com/shop/ultimate-duinobits-starter-kit/#review_form)

Most starter kits will you give a few resistors, some LEDs, and some switches. After a few projects, you’ll need more. Not with this starter kit – there’s enough here to last you a LONG time and hundreds of projects – all in an affordable package that actually costs LESS than most other starter kits.

## Product Description

* Funduino ([Arduino-compatible clone](http://duinobits.com/whats-an-arduino-compatible-clone/)) and USB cable

* [LCD screen](http://duinobits.com/ultimate-starter-kit-guide/lcd-screen/) (Backlit 2×16 character) and pin headers for breadboard mounting
* 8X8 LED dot matrix display
* 1 x 7 segment LED display (single digit)
* [4 x 7 segment LED display](http://duinobits.com/ultimate-starter-kit-guide/4-digit-7-segment-led-display/) (up to four digits)
* 15 LEDs (5 red, 5 yellow, 5 green)
* 15 Resistors (220, 1k, and 10k Ohms)
* Infrared remote control
* Infrared remote receiver
* 2x Tilt switches
* 3x Photoresistors
* Potentiometer (variable resistor)
* Stepper motor and control board

* Servo motor

* 4 pushbutton switches
* Large breadboard
* Passive buzzer (you control the tones)
* Active buzzer (on/off alarm sound)
* 7HC595 Shift register (lets you control more devices than you have output pins)
* LM35 Temperature sensor
* 9v Battery holder
* 8 pin male-female jumper cable
* Various male/male jumper cables for breadboard use
* Resistor values chart sticker
* Bonus component box
* Bonus mini-breadboard shield
